flowchart TD
    %% Entry points
    Start([Mulai / Masuk Website]) --> UserType{Pilih Peran}

    %% User Journey Path
    UserType -->|Pengunjung / Pembeli| Home[Landing Page / Home]
    UserType -->|Admin| Login[Halaman Login Admin]

    %% Home Page Sub-Flows
    Home --> Gallery[GallerySection - Lihat Galeri Bunga]
    Home --> Reviews[ReviewSection - Lihat Review & Kirim Review Baru]
    Home --> Map[MapSection - Lihat Lokasi Toko]
    Home --> About[Halaman About - Tentang Kami]
    Home --> Shop[Halaman Shop - Katalog Produk]
    Home --> ChatbotWidget[Web Chatbot AI Widget]

    %% Chatbot AI Flow
    Shop --> ChatbotWidget
    ChatbotWidget -->|Tanya Bunga / Rekomendasi| AIChatService[AI Chatbot Service - Gemini API]
    AIChatService -.->|Ambil Data Produk & Toko| DB[(Database Dynamic)]
    AIChatService -->|Kirim Jawaban & Link Produk| ChatbotWidget

    %% WhatsApp Chatbot Flow
    WAPath([Chat WA ke Toko]) --> WAWebhook[WhatsApp API Webhook]
    WAWebhook --> AIChatService
    AIChatService -->|Kirim Balasan via WA API| WAPath

    %% Shop & Product Detail Flow
    Shop --> Filter[Filter Kategori & Pencarian Produk]
    Filter --> ProductCard[ProductCard - Klik Detail Produk]
    ProductCard --> ProductDetail[Halaman Detail Produk /product/id]
    
    %% Add to Cart and Checkout
    ProductDetail -->|Pilih Jumlah & Custom| AddToCart[Tambah ke Keranjang]
    Shop -->|Pilih Langsung| AddToCart
    AddToCart --> CartDrawer[CartDrawer / Keranjang Belanja]
    CartDrawer --> CheckoutDrawer[CheckoutDrawer - Formulir Pesanan]
    
    %% Checkout Submission & Payment Gateway Flow
    CheckoutDrawer --> InputForm[Isi Nama, Tanggal Pengambilan & Catatan Custom]
    InputForm --> Validate{Validasi Input?}
    Validate -->|Tidak Valid| ShowError[Tampilkan Error Form]
    ShowError --> InputForm
    Validate -->|Valid| SaveOrderDB[Simpan Data Pesanan ke DB - Status Unpaid]
    
    SaveOrderDB --> PayGateway[Inisiasi Payment Gateway - Midtrans/Xendit]
    PayGateway --> PayProcess{Proses Pembayaran}
    PayProcess -->|Sukses / Gagal / Kadaluarsa| PayCallback[Payment Gateway Webhook/Callback]
    PayCallback --> UpdatePaymentDB[Perbarui Status Pembayaran & Transaksi di DB]
    UpdatePaymentDB --> SendWANotif[Kirim Notifikasi WhatsApp Otomatis ke User & Admin]
    SendWANotif --> FinishOrder([Selesai])

    %% Review submission flow
    Reviews --> WriteReview[Kirim Form Review Baru]
    WriteReview --> SaveReviewDB[Simpan ke DB dengan Status Pending]

    %% Admin Path & Dashboard Flow
    Login --> AuthCheck{Autentikasi?}
    AuthCheck -->|Gagal| Login
    AuthCheck -->|Sukses| AdminDash[Admin Dashboard]

    %% Admin Actions
    AdminDash --> ManageProducts[Kelola Produk CRUD]
    AdminDash --> ManageCategories[Kelola Kategori CRUD]
    AdminDash --> ManageOrders[Kelola Pesanan & Update Status]
    AdminDash --> ManageReviews[Moderasi & Approval Review]
    AdminDash --> ManageGallery[Kelola Foto Galeri]
    AdminDash --> ManageSettings[Kelola Kontak WA & Lokasi Map]
    AdminDash --> ManageAIChatbot[Kelola Konfigurasi AI Chatbot]
    AdminDash --> AISocialAuto[Kelola AI Auto-Post IG/TikTok]

    %% AI Social Media Auto-Post Flow
    AISocialAuto -->|Pilih Produk & Prompt| AICaptionGen[AI Content Generator - Gemini API]
    AICaptionGen -->|Hasilkan Caption & Jadwal Post| SavePostDB[Simpan ke DB Post dengan Status Scheduled]
    CronScheduler[Cron Job Scheduler] -.->|Cek Post Terjadwal| DB
    CronScheduler -->|Kirim Media & Caption ke API| SocialPlatforms[Instagram & TikTok APIs]
    SocialPlatforms -->|Update Status ke Posted/Failed| DB

    %% Database integrations
    ManageProducts -.->|Simpan Perubahan| DB
    ManageCategories -.->|Simpan Perubahan| DB
    ManageOrders -.->|Perbarui Status| DB
    ManageReviews -.->|Approve Review| DB
    ManageGallery -.->|Perbarui Foto| DB
    ManageSettings -.->|Perbarui Konfigurasi| DB
    ManageAIChatbot -.->|Perbarui Parameter AI| DB
    SavePostDB -.-> DB

    %% User loading data
    DB -.->|Ambil Data Dinamis| Shop
    DB -.->|Ambil Review Terpilih| Reviews
    DB -.->|Ambil Foto Galeri| Gallery
    DB -.->|Simpan Pesanan Baru| SaveOrderDB
    DB -.->|Simpan Review Baru| SaveReviewDB
